29/04/2004
BUCHAREST, Romania -- President Ion Iliescu has sharply criticised a report by the NGO Freedom House, local media said Thursday (29 April).
The report questioned the level of progress achieved in securing political rights and civil liberties in Romania.
The president has accused the report's author, Alina Mungiu Pippidi, of bias towards the political right.
(Adevarul - 29/04/04)
